2 Days in the Valley;;54;;62;;R;;Dosmo Pizzo (Danny Aiello), an ordinary guy, finds himself involved in a murder-for-hire scheme. He is betrayed by his partner, the strangely serene Lee Woods (James Spader), who leaves him for dead. Suspecting that Woods will come back to finish him, Dosmo takes an obnoxious art dealer (Greg Cruttwell) and his sweet-natured assistant (Glenne Headly) hostage. Meanwhile, a rookie policeman (Eric Stoltz) investigating the murder begins to suspect that some kind of conspiracy is behind it.;;Drama,Crime;;John Herzfeld;;1996;;Danny Aiello,Glenne Headly,Jeff Daniels,James Spader,Greg Cruttwell,Teri Hatcher,Peter Horton,Marsha Mason,Paul Mazursky,Eric Stoltz,Charlize Theron,Keith Carradine,Louise Fletcher,Austin Pendleton,Kathleen Luong,Michael Jai White,Cress Williams,Lawrence Tierney,Micole Mercurio;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/2_days_in_the_valley